# Run 170 evidence archive — generated run artifacts are reproduced by
# the harness (`scripts/devnet/run_170_governance_proof_production_surface_release_binary.sh`)
# and are not tracked (they contain per-run, machine-specific data such
# as absolute paths, ephemeral helper output, ELF Build IDs, and
# timestamps). Only README.md, summary.txt, and this .gitignore are
# tracked, mirroring the Run 153 / Run 155 / Run 156 / Run 158 /
# Run 160 / Run 162 / Run 164 / Run 166 / Run 168 evidence-archive
# precedent.
/logs/
/data/
/fixtures/
/exit_codes/
/marker_hashes/
/sequence_hashes/
/data_inventories/
/grep_summaries/
/reachability/
/test_results/
/helper_evidence/
/helper_corpus/
/provenance.txt
/fixture_manifest.txt
/scenario_assertions.txt
/negative_invariants.txt
